@page "/faq"

<PageTitle>FAQ - Restaurant Profile</PageTitle>

<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <div class="bg-primary text-white p-5 mb-5 rounded">
                <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
                <p class="text-center text-white mb-0">Everything you need to know about creating your restaurant profile</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
                <p><strong>How do I create a restaurant profile?</strong></p>
                <p>You simply need to be a logged-in user with a confirmed email address. Once your email is verified, you can create your restaurant profile directly from your dashboard.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
                <p><strong>What data is required to create a profile?</strong></p>
                <p>To create a restaurant profile, you will need to provide only restaurant name and address. Everything else can be configured from restaurant edit page after profile is created.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
                <p><strong>Can I manage multiple restaurant locations from one account?</strong></p>
                <p>Yes, you can manage multiple restaurant locations from a single account. Each location will have its own separate profile with individual settings, menus, and reservation systems. You can easily switch between locations from your dashboard.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
                <p><strong>What photos should I add to my restaurant profile?</strong></p>
                <p>We recommend adding high-quality photos of your restaurant's interior, exterior, signature dishes, and dining atmosphere. A professional logo and cover photo are also essential. Photos showcasing your team and special events can help create a more personal connection with potential guests.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
                <p><strong>What are the technical requirements for photos?</strong></p>
                <p>Photos should be in JPG, PNG. The maximum file size is 5 MB per image. </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
                <p><strong>How do I add a menu to my restaurant profile?</strong></p>
                <p>Navigate to the "Menu" section in restaurant edit page. You can add menu items by entering dish names, descriptions, prices, and photos.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
                <p><strong>Can I mark allergens and dietary information in the menu?</strong></p>
                <p>We recommend using dish tags for this, or writing it in dish description</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
                <p><strong>How do I enable the reservation acceptance system?</strong></p>
                <p>Go to Restaurant edit page and then to settings tab</p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center mt-5">
                <a href="/homepage" class="button button--lg button--primary" style="text-decoration: none;">Go Back</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
